comments: Fournier (ORL) does not dislodge Joseph (SAC) on his drive to the basket.  Joseph loses his balance on his own.
Joseph (SAC) makes contact to Fournier's (ORL) body during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Vucevic (ORL) makes marginal contact to Bagley III's (SAC) body during his shooting motion on the shot attempt.
Bagley III (SAC) establishes his legal screening position in Gordon's (ORL) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
After the hand-off Gordon (ORL) establishes his screening position and gives Fox (SAC) room to avoid the contact.
Vucevic (ORL) lifts his pivot foot prior to the shot attempt.
Fox (SAC) does not extend his off arm into Fultz's (ORL) body as he gathers the ball and begins his upward shooting motion.
Fox (SAC) cleanly dislodges the ball away from Fournier (ORL) on his driving shot attempt.
Bjelica (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Fultz (ORL) and absorbs the contact.
Bagley III (SAC) briefly engages and disengages with Vucevic (ORL) off ball.
Vucevic (ORL) makes contact to Fox's (SAC) body which affects his driving shot attempt.
Joseph (SAC) has his defensive position established against Gordon (ORL) but he does not deliver contact as he begins his upward shooting motion.
During the inbound pass Iwundu (ORL) and Barnes (SAC) both reach for the ball and as Barnes receives the pass and attempts the shot Iwundu makes marginal contact to his front.
